CMPSC440: Operating Systems
5/22/14 - Deadlock & Distributed Systems
========================================


Strategies for handling deadlock:
	+ Ignore the problem ("ostrich algorithm")
	+ Detection & recovery
		- Resource allocation graph
			1. Form a RAG
			2. Run cycle detection
				* Mathematica has a cycle detection algorithm!
			3a. If a cycle exists, we can...
				-> Stop a process. Which one?
					* the one which uses the most resources
					* the one using the fewest resources
					* the one running the longest
					* the one running the shortest